If Statement-
1)@if(condition){
  //statement
  }
2)@if(condition){
  //statement
  }
  else
  {
   //statement
  }


Ternary Operator-
@(condition?statement1:statement2)\

For loop-
@for(int i=1;i<=10;i++)
{
//statements
}

Foreach Loop-
@foreach(var item in collection)
{
//statements
}

Directives in Razor-
1) @using(Used to add model class and namespace etc)
2) @model(Used to provide type of model)
